{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be cozy and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CozyFlow - Your SaaS Companion</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fdf6f2;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #d9534f;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-bottom: 8px solid #c34a47;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #d9534f;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #d9534f;\n            color: #fff;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #fff8f0;\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #d9534f;\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid #d9534f;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #d9534f;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .testimonials {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #fdfcf8;\n        }\n        .testimonials h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #d9534f;\n        }\n        .testimonial-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            font-style: italic;\n            position: relative;\n            border-top: 5px solid #d9534f;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item footer {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .footer {\n            background-color: #d9534f;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 80px;\n        }\n        .footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .footer a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Subtle Animations */\n        @keyframes fadeInUp {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        .hero h1, .hero p, .cta-button {\n            animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out 0.5s forwards;\n            opacity: 0;\n        }\n\n        .features h2, .feature-item, .testimonials h2, .testimonial-item {\n            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;\n            opacity: 0;\n        }\n\n        .features .feature-item:nth-child(1),\n        .testimonials .testimonial-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }\n        .features .feature-item:nth-child(2),\n        .testimonials .testimonial-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }\n        .features .feature-item:nth-child(3),\n        .testimonials .testimonial-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>CozyFlow: Your Calm in the SaaS Storm</h1>\n        <p>Streamline your workflow with a touch of warmth and simplicity. Designed for comfort, built for productivity.</p>\n        <a href=\"#features\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Features</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"features\">\n        <h2>Unwind and Achieve</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Intuitive Design</h3>\n                <p>Navigate your tasks with ease. Our clean and cozy interface feels like home.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Seamless Integration</h3>\n                <p>Connect your favorite tools without the fuss. CozyFlow works harmoniously with your existing setup.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Focus on What Matters</h3>\n                <p>Minimize distractions and maximize your output. We help you stay centered on your goals.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"testimonials\" id=\"testimonials\">\n        <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>\n        <div class=\"testimonial-grid\">\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"CozyFlow has transformed my chaotic workday into a peaceful, productive experience. It's like a warm cup of tea for my business!\"</p>\n                <footer>- Alex Johnson, Creative Director</footer>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"I love how simple and effective CozyFlow is. The red accents are a nice touch, making it feel very inviting.\"</p>\n                <footer>- Sarah Chen, Freelance Designer</footer>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <p>&copy; 2023 CozyFlow. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Made with <span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">&#10084;</span> and a dash of comfort. <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}